shitty little splash generator.


Usage: mksplash [options] region:url url url region:url ...
	where a region is the template location to put the posts in,
	defaulting to 'default'. Each url is an rss feed full of posts.


Options:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -o OUTFILE, --output=OUTFILE
                        File to write
  -v, --verbose         DEBUG to STDOUT
  -d DEPTH, --depth=DEPTH
                        Max number of posts per url.
  -l LENGTH, --length=LENGTH
                        Max number of characters per url (truncates at
                        whitespace).
  -t TEMPLATES, --templates=TEMPLATES
                        Location to search for template files.
